                    <div>
                      <h2>Eligibility</h2>
                      <div class="view section-layout-standard forms row section">
                        <h3 class="first-only col-xs-12">Right to work in the UK</h3>
                        <div>
                          <div class="view group-layout-simple forms field-group col-xs-12">
                            <div>
                              <div class="view eligibility bootstrap octane-ats">
                                <p>We need to confirm that you are eligible to work in the UK, if you are invited to an interview you will need to bring with you one of the following.</p>
                                <p>
                                  <strong>If you are from the UK you will need to bring one of the following:</strong>
                                </p>
                                <ul>
                                  <li>UK Passport</li>
                                  <li>Full UK birth certificate or full UK adoption certificate with proof of your NI number</li>
                                  <li>A document issued by a government agency</li>
                                  <li>NI card or previous company P45/P60 showing your NI number</li>
                                </ul>
                                <p>
                                  <strong>If you are from the EU you will need to bring one of the following:</strong>
                                </p>
                                <ul>
                                  <li>EU Issued Passport</li>
                                  <li>National Identity card</li>
                                </ul>
                                <p>
                                  <strong>If you are from elsewhere in the world:</strong>
                                </p>
                                <ul>
                                  <li>Passport with documentation of Permanent Residence or Right to Work</li>
                                </ul>
                                <p>Further information can be found on 
                                  <a href="http://www.ukba.homeoffice.gov.uk" title="UK Visas and Immigration">www.ukba.homeoffice.gov.uk</a>
                                </p>
                              </div>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                          <div class="view group-layout-simple forms field-group col-xs-12">
                            <div>
                              <div class="view field-checkbox forms field input checkbox">
                                <label>
